# trackcovid

The API for the tarckcovid app.

## User [/users/{user_id}] 

+ Parameters
    + user_id (number) - ID of the user in the form of an integer

### Retrieve an user [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
        {
            "user": {
                "id": "999", 
                "fbId": "<fb-provided-id>",
                "cases": [
                    {
                            "id": 123,
                            "fbId": "<fb-provided-id>",
                            "postalCode": "xxxx-xx",
                            "geo": {
                                "lat": 0,
                                "lon": 0
                            },
                            "condition": "normal",
                            "timestamp": "2012-04-23T18:25:43.511Z"
                        },
                    {
                            "id": 123,
                            "fbId": "<fb-provided-id>",
                            "postalCode": "xxxx-xx",
                            "geo": {
                                "lat": 0,
                                "lon": 0
                            },
                            "condition": "normal",
                            "timestamp": "2012-04-23T18:25:43.511Z"
                        }
                        
                ],
                "network": {
                    "direct": [
                        {
                            "condition": "infected",
                            "value": 10
                        },
                        {
                            "condition": "quarentine",
