## Cases Collection [/cases]

### List All Cases [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "case": {
                    "id": 123,
                    "fbId": "<fb-provided-id>",
                    "postalCode": "xxxx-xx",
                    "geo": {
                        "lat": 0,
                        "lon": 0
                    },
                    "condition": "normal|infected|quarentine|symptomatic|recovered",
                    "timestamp": "2012-04-23T18:25:43.511Z"
                }
            }
        ]
        
        + Response 401 (application/json)
        {
          "error": "error.unauthorized"
        }

### Create a New Case [POST]

Create a new case

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "case": {
                "fbId": "<fb-provided-id>",
                "postalCode": "xxxx-xx",
                "geo": {
                    "lat": 0,
                    "lon": 0
                },
                "condition": "normal|infected|quarentine|symptomatic|recovered",
                "timestamp": "2012-04-23T18:25:43.511Z"
            }
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /cases/123

    + Body

            {
                "case": {
                    "id": 123,
                    "fbId": "<fb-provided-id>",
                    "postalCode": "xxxx-xx",
                    "geo": {
                        "lat": 0,
                        "lon": 0
                    },
                    "condition": "normal|infected|quarentine|symptomatic|recovered",
                    "timestamp": "2012-04-23T18:25:43.511Z"
                }
            }

+ Response 401 (application/json)
        {
          "error": "error.unauthorized"
        }

